你能够调用以下的API:
[['RetirementPlanner.get_current_expenses', {'name': 'RetirementPlanner.get_current_expenses', 'description': 'Retrieve the current monthly expenses of the user.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'monthlyExpenses', 'description': 'The current monthly expenses of the user.'}]}], ['RetirementPlanner.get_retirement_age', {'name': 'RetirementPlanner.get_retirement_age', 'description': 'Retrieve the user's expected retirement age.', 'required_parameters': [], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'retirementAge', 'description': 'The expected retirement age of the user.'}]}], ['RetirementPlanner.get_cost_of_living_index', {'name': 'RetirementPlanner.get_cost_of_living_index', 'description': 'Retrieve the cost of living index for a specific location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location for which the cost of living index is required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'costOfLivingIndex', 'description': 'The cost of living index for the specified location.'}]}], ['RetirementPlanner.get_retirement_benefits', {'name': 'RetirementPlanner.get_retirement_benefits', 'description': 'Retrieve the retirement benefits available in a specific location.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'location', 'type': 'STRING', 'description': 'The location for which the retirement benefits are required.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'retirementBenefits', 'description': 'The retirement benefits available in the specified location.'}]}], ['RetirementPlanner.evaluate_retirement_quality', {'name': 'RetirementPlanner.evaluate_retirement_quality', 'description': 'Evaluate the quality of retirement life based on current expenses, retirement age, cost of living index, and retirement benefits.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'currentExpenses', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The current monthly expenses of the user.'}, {'name': 'retirementAge', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The expected retirement age of the user.'}, {'name': 'costOfLivingIndex', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The cost of living index for the specified location.'}, {'name': 'retirementBenefits', 'type': 'NUMBER', 'description': 'The retirement benefits available in the specified location.'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'retirementQuality', 'description': 'The evaluated quality of retirement life.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
